{"tid":254933,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"被毓民掃地出門後，陳雲話：革命黨失敗之後，必須清算。","createTime":"2017-05-23T14:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T14:05:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab5f8eae828630806323ce3d87fc636449b40ea","tid":254933,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"自己被人清左, 都咁厚臉皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155240602202225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwan.chin.75%2Fposts%2F10155240602202225&d=kH2M4iXnzlAaiIbtGoJs1gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ef2b5e9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wan.chin.75/posts/10155240602202225</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：革命黨失敗之後，必須清算。清算之後，整固實力，再出發。<br />\n反革命的人，最怕被清算。因為他們從來只是想霸佔革命果實，一旦被清算出去，就沒法享用下次的革命果實了。"},{"pid":"b6a62c26f7f06959eafac096911e8c86b016171a","tid":254933,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"Wan Chin 反革命的，返回泛民長毛港獨那邊吧。Back to where you belong.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/author/陳雲/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fauthor%2F%E9%99%B3%E9%9B%B2%2F&d=kH2M4iXnzlAaiIbtGoJs1gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=92903e07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fauthor%2F%E9%99%B3%E9%9B%B2%2F&h=d818a54d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/author/陳雲/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}